{"tid":757964,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我迫不及待好想玩玩了","createTime":"2018-07-27T09:26:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-27T09:34:21.000Z","uid":2794,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b61680ba03d84ef9e680711738ed469ee8f26d3d","tid":757964,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:26:28.000Z","msg":"想通了，即將要和社會接軌， <br />\n就職後要拼盡全力 賺錢，拿取權力。 <br />\n會首先經 香港公開大學BBA(C&amp;G) FT. 進場,先拿Degree。 <br />\n然後一邊工作一邊拿Master，以最快速度上位。 <br />\n成功KO第一捅金後，我才能繼續實現夢想，理想。 <br />\n(搞樂團，養孩子，父母，去幫有需要的人) <br />\n4年 Business Law, 將來就可以用法律監管公司各個部門。 <br />\n又要負責幫公司和 港交所，稅務局聯繫。<br />\n更加可以有能力為公司制定未來政策。<br />\n表現好的話可以入董事會。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n簡直是公司主力核心。 <br />\n我迫不及待好想玩玩了。"},{"pid":"5cc16cfc963afc4020b3df9eb1bd6ba3a4a5ac63","tid":757964,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"你poly mk"},{"pid":"e460ebbc1e5b295a89572fbc68c3ab8ababca07c","tid":757964,"uid":35667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:28:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"683fab962179d2d80f0197bfc8a04e8b1d123ba0","tid":757964,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cc16cfc963afc4020b3df9eb1bd6ba3a4a5ac63","tid":757964,"uid":14719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:27:51.000Z","msg":"你poly mk"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"依家讀ou"},{"pid":"f7585a26f4c5ae88f0debba0cd8056ac77b0eacd","tid":757964,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-27T09:29:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/27/172942_10442f2fbbf6375aab19f6b499e9210e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F27%2F172942_10442f2fbbf6375aab19f6b499e9210e.png&h=5f4133d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e086f125180361b7319e8406c30f577f42d911a","tid":757964,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0